{"atom_id": "ig34_p0347_a020", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 347, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "TU – Assumptions", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "If the data collection does not support this approach (i.e., measurements of split tumors/lesions are reported as a summary under the "parent" tumor/lesion), then it may not be possible to include a record in the TU domain.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.4", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0347_a021", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 347, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "TU – Assumptions", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In this situation, the assessments of split and merge tumors/lesions would be represented only in the TR domain.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.4", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0347_a022", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 347, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "TU – Assumptions", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "3. For some response criteria (e.g., Lugano, Kumar IMWG 2016), tumors are assessed by location of interest. A record is required in TU in order to link the assessments of the particular location of interest in TR.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.4", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0347_a023", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 347, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "TU – Assumptions", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "This example represents tumors assessed by location of interest.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.4", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0347_a024", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 347, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "TU – Assumptions", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In TULNKID = \"L01\", the spleen is identified as a location of interest using computerized tomography (CT) scan.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.4", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0347_a025", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 347, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "TU – Assumptions", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In TULNKID = \"L04\", the whole body is identified as a location of interest using positron emission tomography (PET) scan.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.4", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0347_a026", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 347, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "TU – Assumptions", "atom_type": "TABLE_HEADER", "verbatim": "| TULNKID | TUTESTCD | TUTEST | TULOCL TUORLOC LOCATION OF INTEREST | TULOC SPLEEN | TUMETHOD CT SCAN |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.4", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0347_a027", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 347, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "TU – Assumptions", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| L01 | TUMIDENT | Tumor Identification | | | |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.4", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
